    <briefdescription>
<para>Base class for table metadata changes using builder pattern. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This base class allows storing different types of <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdate" kindref="compound">PendingUpdate</ref> operations in the same collection (e.g., in <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1Transaction" kindref="compound">Transaction</ref>). It provides the common <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdate_1a0643491619bb8e88a60943e5546adcb6" kindref="member">Commit()</ref> interface that all updates share.</para>
<para>This matches the Java Iceberg pattern where BaseTransaction stores a List&lt;PendingUpdate&gt; without type parameters. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
